	Directive		Data Type
	---------		---------
	.ascii			Text string.
	.asciz			Null-terminated text string.
	.byte			Byte value.
	.double			Double-precission floating point number.
	.float			Single-precission floating point number.
	.int			32-bit integer.
	.long			64-bit integer.
	.octa			16-byte integer.
	.quad			8-byte integer.
	.short			16-bit integer.
	.single			Single precission floating point. Same as float.
	.equ			Indicates constant value. Works very much like the #define directive of C.

	.comm			Declares common memory area for data that is not initialized.
	.lcomm			Declares local common memory area for data that is not initialized.
